===Transitive verb===
'''to fancy'''

#(''old-fashioned'') To [[suppose]].
#:''I fancy you'll want something to drink after your long journey''
#(''British''; ''colloquial'') To be sexually attracted to.
#:''I fancy you in that hat.''

