'''fancy!''' (''also'' '''fancy that!''', '''well, fancy!''' and '''well, fancy that!''')
#Expressing surprise at hearing information that is not as was expected.
#: ''Fancy that! I saw Elizabeth Bennett and Mr. Darcy kissing in the garden.''

